<div class="title">Adderall.. Love it and Hate It</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamine (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Danielle&Exact=1">Danielle</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Danielle. "Adderall.. Love it and Hate It: An Experience with Amphetamine (Adderall) (exp13092)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 25, 2002. erowid.org/exp/13092</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
